Package: argyle
Type: Package
Title: Basic interface and QC for genotypes from Illumina Infinium arrays
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2015-10-13
Author: Andrew P Morgan
Maintainer: Andrew P Morgan  <andrew.parker.morgan@gmail.com>
Description: Some useful stuff for handling genotypes (and underlying
    hybridization intensity data) from Illumina Infinium arrays.
